        "subject": "LU-3192 clio: fix LU-481 in different way.",
        "message": "LU-3192 clio: fix LU-481 in different way.\n\nthis is not correct to kick transient pages off the CLIO cache,\nbecause we may get 2 sets of pages in osc_build_req(), cachable\nand transient ones.\n\nThus, just delete the page before being freed in page_find.\n\nChange-Id: Ifbcca5216ce651fc151c9ba893824b4e61d16ad4\nSigned-off-by: Vitaly Fertman <vitaly_fertman@xyratex.com>\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-859\n"
